rtnerships with the insurance and finance community the project is aimed at becoming the standard of experiential learning within the insurance and financial services sector for mbas examples include optimization of portfolios which are subject to constraints defining technology solutions to the fiduciary responsibilities in financial services efficient organizational platforms adroit uses of cutting edge technology identifying and acting on market inefficiencies and employing dynamic financial analysis in the property casualty industry mediaedit in july  stone was selected by the nasdaq ceo signature series as a notable ceo and had a corresponding interview stone was also featured on cnbcs fast money a halftime report reviewing daily trends and breakthroughs in the financial industry stone was further selected for an exclusive interview on interesting people with ed sutkowski in  stone was named on institutional investor’s  all american executive team best midcap ceos list in the category of technology media  communication for the software sector referencesedit  forbes the worlds billionaires  william stone april   bill stone linkedin page linkedin retrieved  february    ssc technologies  years ssc tech   william stone forbes retrieved    anniversary th ssc celebrates  years of innovation wwwssctechcom retrieved    ssc to establish new fund administration and technology center in evansville indiana nasdaqssnc investorssctechcom retrieved    ssc expands evansville indiana office space nasdaqssnc investorssctechcom retrieved    ssc portia expands business operations leveraging sscs center of excellence in evansville nasdaqssnc investorssctechcom retrieved    technologies ssc ssc technologies and university of southern indiana launch investment accounting accelerator at the romain college of business globenewswire news room retrieved          httpwwwcnbccomidplayvideo    the  allamerica executive team ceos go long on value wwwinstitutionalinvestorcom retrieved   exter