e foundation also gives college scholarships one of the beneficiaries is the demographer pollster and political pundit elliott stonecipher of shreveport louisiana who entered the boy of the year competition in the late s at the national boys clubs competition stone was a supporter of the napoleon hill foundation which he directed for forty years and to which his estate contributes funding stone celebrated his th birthday with a gift of  to the university of illinois at chicago stone provided much of the initial funding for the selfhelp organization grow stone was inducted into the horatio alger association of distinguished americans and was a freemason w clement stone once stated “regardless of what you are or what you have been you can still become what you may want to be” referencesedit  a b c d e f g h douglas martin september   clement stone dies at  built empire on optimism new york times retrieved  w clement stone who parlayed  in savings into an insurance empire that financed millions of dollars of contributions to the campaigns of richard m nixon and hundreds of millions to charities died on tuesday in evanston ill he was  and lived in winnetka ill william clement stone was born in chicago on may   his father died when he was  leaving the family impoverished by gambling losses at the age of  he began hawking newspapers on chicagos south side while his mother worked as a dressmaker at  he owned his own newsstand   a b c stone w clement  the success system that never fails pdf mb lightning source inc isbn    hill napoleon  think and grow rich inside front cover page fawcett books new york isbn   a b c d e httpfinancialsoftwarecomafforgsdocumentsvolissuepdf  ace completes acquisition of combined insurance company of america acelimitedcom  retrieved    hill napoleon  the think and grow rich action pack plume isbn   a b c john c  maxwell success magazine success magazine retrieved    a b improve your thinking  w clement stone to mark his th june   savage terry ch